>‧裝備 龍輝護符「暴風之譽」吧。<br>‧到「真‧耶夢加得的試煉」的任務頁面點選「詳細」，確認有利於與BOSS戰鬥的提示吧。<br>‧參考看看「真‧耶夢加得的試煉　中級」的推薦隊伍編制吧。</div><hr><div><details open=""><summary>「真‧耶夢加得的試煉　中級」推薦隊伍編制</summary><div>■編制例①<br>角色：主角<br>武器：雷瓦汀<br>龍族：凱爾貝洛斯、木花開耶姬、索狄亞克（育龍庭園Ver.）<br>護符：①暴風之譽／②光輝之霸主、天才的靈光乍現<table style="width: calc(100% - 24px); margin-left: 12px;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 18%; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);">角色<br></td><td style="width: 26%; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:10px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/14c7d3e3f9e3508f805178100bf5de60.png" style="width: 48px; height: 48px;"></span><br></td><td style="width: 50%;">主角<br></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 20%; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);">武器<br></td><td style="width: 26%; text-align: center;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/8a103c4b9ff2fb1b0b759642821bbec9.png" class="img-enemy" style="width: 48px; height: 48px;"><br></td><td style="width: 50%;">雷瓦汀<br></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 17.451%; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);">龍族<br></td><td style="width: 26%; text-align: center;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/37ccc946be118ab07b2b5351af51b51a.png" class="img-enemy" style="width: 48px; height: 48px;"><br><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/93cea341bc5051de869d3b46fde59f30.png" class="img-enemy" style="width: 48px; height: 48px;"><br><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/d9d4ccb57be57ae925a5dfce45eddb60.png" class="img-enemy" style="width: 48px; height: 48px;"><br></td><td style="width: 50%;">凱爾貝洛斯<br>木花開耶姬<br>索狄亞克（育龍庭園Ver.）<br></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 18%; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(204, 204, 204);">護符<br></td><td style="width: 26%; text-align: center;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/935ada61f0eb